    "spell": {
        "name": "Wilding Word",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "Your patron's majesty\u2014or their displeasure\u2014comes in a growl from your throat, making other creatures reluctant to harm you. The target must attempt a Will save; if the creature is an animal, fungus, or plant, it takes a \u20131 circumstance penalty to its save.",
